data.description: Why Not Live in Harmony! This house and community has so much to offer. The house itself is one of the largest floor-plans built by DR Horton just a few years ago.This lovely home greets you as walk up - cool stamped concrete in the back yard of the home including a Gas Fire Pit, concrete walk-way was added to wrap around to the back porch, Newly Poured Apron on Driveway. Once you enter the home, up front is a spacious Main Level Bedroom with Full Bath steps away. Towards the back of the house you will have plenty of room in the kitchen with granite counters and Bright White cabinets. Large Corner Pantry. Kitchen island will seat 4 at the counter plus a dining area with access to the back yard. This opens to the living room where you can cozy up to the fireplace.  Upstairs is wonderfully designed with a stunning primary suite with sitting area, huge walk-in closet. For convenience you also have the laundry upstairs, 3 additional bedrooms (they are good size too!) and a loft perfect for a gaming room or additional living space. Let's talk about all the amenities this community has to Offer! There is a heated outdoor pool with a splash pad and unlike many communities there is also a hot tub, full fitness center with a golf simulator! Residents can rent out the center for events. There are parks with volleyball and basketball courts, playgrounds, picnic areas, and walking paths!
